reviewText: Good old movie, brought back to life
Always great to add Davey & Goliath to my collection.

This is a series I want my kids to see, I'm so glad Bridgestone Multimedia Group is releasing them.  The titles on this one, according to their website, are: "Big Apple," "The Bridge," "The Jickets (a.k.a. The Gang)," "The Lemonade Stand," "Hocus Pocus," "Good Neighbor".  Of these, only "Hocus Pocus" is new to DVD.
